reviewText: It's a good dancing tape for elder!
this is a good tape to start with. they teach at a very good pace. i learned quite a few dances.
Excellent tape to watch and participate with if you are looking to learn some really fun line dances.  I recommend this tape for any age group that is looking to put a bit of pep in their step!
I actually like this one the best.  It makes me work harder to learn these dances than the other, but they are both good
I'm 56 and am sick of buying workout videos that are too hard for someone my age, but this video, wait till you're in your 70's.  It's really boring and slow.
I really liked this tape. It was easy to learn the dances from the tape. I would recommend this tape for everyone
